\newlabel{fig:booking}{{3}{10}{Relational mapping --- Booking, Payments \& Ratings. \texttt {Payments} and \texttt {Payouts} carry \emph {no} database foreign keys by design (loose references); the booking's \texttt {(ConsultantId, ScheduledStartAt)} filtered-unique index prevents double-booking}{figure.caption.4}{}}
